# Linux Practice Labs

## Lab 1

Objective

Practice file management commands.

Commands Used

mkdir LinuxPractice

cd LinuxPractice

touch notes.txt

cp notes.txt backup.txt

mv backup.txt notes_backup.txt

rm notes_backup.txt

find . -name "*.txt"

Skills Learned

- Creating directories
- Creating files
